Evermore is a trip planning app which can create and execute multiple searches and present the results all on a single map.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.barryholroyd.evermore
Top-level package for Evermore -- primarily initialization and configuration.
com.barryholroyd.evermore.contacts
Provides access to the contacts in the user's local address book.
com.barryholroyd.evermore.contacts.api
This package provides an API to the database which other app methods can use so that they are isolated from the details of the database (e.g., its schema).
com.barryholroyd.evermore.contacts.database
This module handles all of the direct interactions with the SQLite database.
com.barryholroyd.evermore.contacts.service
Reads contacts from the local address book and loads them into the SQLite database.
